"content": "<h2>Uses of straw</h2>\n<h3>As animal bedding and fodder</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:32\">GEN 24:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:22-Gen24:25\">GEN 24:22–24:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg19:16-Judg19:19\">JDG 19:16–19:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:27-1Kgs4:28\">1KI 4:27–4:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:7\">ISA 11:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:25\">ISA 65:25</a></p>\n<h3>In brickmaking</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod5:6-Exod5:7\">EXO 5:6–5:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod5:10-Exod5:13\">EXO 5:10–5:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod5:15-Exod5:18\">EXO 5:15–5:18</a></p>\n<h2>The lightness and fragility of straw</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job21:18\">JOB 21:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:26-Job41:29\">JOB 41:26–41:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:24\">ISA 5:24</a></p>\n<h2>Straw is of little value</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:11\">ISA 33:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:10\">ISA 25:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:28\">JER 23:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:10-1Cor3:15\">1CO 3:10–3:15</a></p>",
